  "siteName": "谷歌开发者",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100113252\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.2972222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"172\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e1d622a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FicFp8MFO4IKySovZHlPtBwXafoecQSMEQW477IJmeLicz1G8h29ToF7DHCn15BTD8gEJJy0uVOIMU07eGKvMzsdQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dzv09lk56\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzj1eazh4\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mdwzj1eq1z61\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);font-style: italic;\">作者 / 开发者关系工程师 Don Turner</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1ub3o\">在应用中的不同屏幕之间导航理应简单明了。然而，构建稳健、可扩展且赏心悦目的导航体验却并非易事。多年来，Jetpack Navigation 库一直是开发者的重要工具，但随着 Android 界面格局的演变，尤其是 Jetpack Compose 的兴起，我们意识到是时候探索一种全新的解决方案了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u1g1v\"><span leaf=\"\">我们将在本文为您介绍新推出的&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Jetpack Navigation 3</span>，这是一个专为 Compose 打造的全新导航库。为简洁起见，我们将其简称为 Nav3。这个库采用了<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">声明式编程模型</span>和&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">Compose 状态</span>作为其基本构建模块。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">声明式编程模型</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/develop/ui/compose/mental-model\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.android.com/develop/ui/compose/mental-model</a></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">Compose 状态</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/develop/ui/compose/state\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.android.com/develop/ui/compose/state</a></span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;width: auto;height: auto;margin-left: 15px;border-left: 1px dotted rgb(70, 70, 70);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;line-height: 0;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 14px 0% -7px;transform: translate3d(-4px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <p style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 7px;width: 7px;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 3px 0px inset;\">\n         <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">为什么要推出新的导航库？</span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u22rc\">之前的 Jetpack Navigation 库 (有时也称为 Nav2，因为它是第二个主版本) 最初是在 2018 年发布的，彼时还没有 AndroidX 和 Compose 这两个框架。虽然 Nav2 已经很好地实现了最初目标，但我们了解到，在与现代 Compose 开发模式结合使用时，Nav2 存在一些限制。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u21f5\"><span leaf=\"\">其中一个关键的限制是仅支持间接观察返回堆栈状态。这意味着可能存在两个事实来源，从而导致应用状态出现不一致的情况。此外，Nav2 的&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">NavHost</span>&nbsp;被设计为仅显示一个目标位置 (即返回堆栈中的最顶层目标位置) 以填充可用空间。这使得实现同时显示多个内容窗格的自适应布局 (例如大屏幕上的列表-详情布局) 变得困难。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100113251\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.46296296296296297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 268px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/icFp8MFO4IKySovZHlPtBwXafoecQSMEQdmlPKibAS2QCVvGCKibKuCIXC9icNJXY4YJ6qIrIkXicOnnCaiav73OpoNA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1322\" data-cropy2=\"612.9688581314878\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"296\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4b2d1009&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FicFp8MFO4IKyZIURZTxZNq1giaNd9SxUcgGxFm8mpV246E37DoycjDyQHud7aw9ptQmLYtUFlmibVTNJL8TnFdRicg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26randomid%3D8qknd646\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdxxrr5znjo\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mdxxrr6e1dhd\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\">△ 从单窗格布局切换到多窗格布局可能会带来导航方面的挑战</span></span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;width: auto;height: auto;margin-left: 15px;border-left: 1px dotted rgb(70, 70, 70);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;line-height: 0;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 14px 0% -7px;transform: translate3d(-4px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <p style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 7px;width: 7px;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 3px 0px inset;\">\n         <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 67, 53);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">创立原则</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u1rlb\">Nav3 基于以下原则构建而成，旨在提供更大的灵活性并提高开发者掌控力:</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u1ozx\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">您掌控返回堆栈</span>: 作为开发者，您将拥有并控制返回堆栈，而不是将控制权交给库。这是一个简单的列表，由 Compose 状态支持。具体而言，Nav3 期望您的返回堆栈为&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">SnapshotStateList&lt;T&gt;</span>，其中&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">T</span>&nbsp;可以是您选择的任何类型。您可以通过添加或删除项目 (<span textstyle=\"\">T</span>) 来进行导航，状态的变化会被 Nav3 的界面观测到，并自动反映在其界面上。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u1unr\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">告别繁琐</span>: 我们深知您不喜欢导航库具有无法访问的内部组件和状态的 \"黑匣子\" 式设计。Nav3 的设计秉承开放性和可扩展性原则，为您提供构建模块和实用的默认设置。如果您想要自定义导航行为，可以<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">深入到更低的层级</span>，创建您自己的组件和自定义设置。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u5ki\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">选择您的构建模块</span>: Nav3 并没有将所有行为嵌入到库中，而是提供了更小巧的组件，您可以组合这些组件来创建更复杂的功能。我们还准备了<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">操作指南</span>，其中介绍了如何组合组件来解决常见的导航挑战。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100113250\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.3712962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"215\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4d65f3ce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FicFp8MFO4IKySovZHlPtBwXafoecQSMEQ5zhcnwsU5Q77VxZP6JVtjhgWdZMpRX26fNxskoyxkLpM4sTdBTlpcw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3D9qevj51g\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u111e\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\">△ Nav3 Display 组件观测开发者拥有的返回堆栈的变化</span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">深入到更低的层级</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\">h</span><span leaf=\"\">ttps://developer.android.com/develop/ui/compose/layering</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">操作指南</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"http://github.com/android/nav3-recipes\" target=\"_blank\">http://github.com/android/nav3-recipes</a></span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;width: auto;height: auto;margin-left: 15px;border-left: 1px dotted rgb(70, 70, 70);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;line-height: 0;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 14px 0% -7px;transform: translate3d(-4px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <p style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 7px;width: 7px;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 3px 0px inset;\">\n         <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: le f t;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 188, 4);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">关键功能</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1udsw\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">动画</span>: 内置的过渡动画可用于实现目标位置的切换，包括<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">预测性返回</span>。此外，它还拥有<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">支持自定义动画行为的灵活 API</span>，允许在应用和单个屏幕级别覆写动画。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1uyf5\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">自适应布局</span>: 通过使用<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">灵活布局 API</span>&nbsp;(名为&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">Scenes</span>)，您可在同一布局中渲染多个目标位置 (例如，大屏设备上的列表-详情布局)。您可借此轻松地在单窗格和多窗格布局之间切换。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1uhg6\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">状态范围限定</span>: 能够将状态限定在返回堆栈中的目标位置范围内，同时还可通过<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">专用 Jetpack lifecycle 库</span>提供可选的&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">ViewModel</span>&nbsp;支持。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u1gnh\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">模块化</span>: API 设计允许将导航代码拆分到多个模块中。这缩短了构建时间并使各个功能模块之间的职责划分更加清晰。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mdy4eovd22zc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100113261\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"1.936923076923077\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"650\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;background-color: transparent;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97582fa4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FicFp8MFO4IKyZIURZTxZNq1giaNd9SxUcgJjR8MGFTAZlJLuLg1VI4mKQQ5lSicbiajWAGb1NibRBr43sHmdicbGdoLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Ders81pj3\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdxyarzb246a\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mdxyarzn1xjg\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\">△ 可以轻松实现自定义动画和预测性返回，并且易于针对各个目标位置进行单独的覆写</span></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">预测性返回</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/develop/ui/compose/system/predictive-back\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.android.com/develop/ui/compose/system/predictive-back</a></span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">支持自定义动画行为的灵活 API</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/guide/navigation/navigation-3/animate-destinations\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.android.com/guide/navigation/navigation-3/animate-destinations</a></span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">灵活布局 API</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/guide/navigation/navigation-3/custom-layouts\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.android.com/guide/navigation/navigation-3/custom-layouts</a></span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">专用 Jetpack lifecycle 库</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/guide/navigation/navigation-3/save-state\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.android.com/guide/navigation/navigation-3/save-state</a><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mdxy9ifj-2l1xyc\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#scoping</a>-viewmodels</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;width: auto;height: auto;margin-left: 15px;border-left: 1px dotted rgb(70, 70, 70);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;line-height: 0;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 14px 0% -7px;transform: translate3d(-4px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <p style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 7px;width: 7px;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 3px 0px inset;\">\n         <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: le f t;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">基本代码示例</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1uy7n\">为了帮助您了解 Nav3 的工作原理，我们准备了简短的代码示例。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n   <li></li>\n  </ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"kotlin\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">// Define the routes in your app and any arguments.</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">data</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">object</span>&nbsp;Home</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">data</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">class</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__title\">Product</span>(<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">val</span>&nbsp;id: String)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">// Create a back stack, specifying the route the app should start with.</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">val</span>&nbsp;backStack = remember { mutableStateListOf&lt;Any&gt;(Home) }</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">// A NavDisplay displays your back stack. Whenever the back stack changes, the display updates.</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">NavDisplay(</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; backStack = backStack,</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">// Specify what should happen when the user goes back</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; onBack = { backStack.removeLastOrNull() },</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">// An entry provider converts a route into a NavEntry which contains the content for that route.</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; entryProvider = { route -&gt;</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">when</span>&nbsp;(route) {</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">is</span>&nbsp;Home -&gt; NavEntry(route) {</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Column {</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Text(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"Welcome to Nav3\"</span>)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Button(onClick = {</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">// To navigate to a new route, just add that route to the back stack</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; backStack.add(Product(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"123\"</span>))</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }) {</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Text(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"Click to navigate\"</span>)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">is</span>&nbsp;Product -&gt; NavEntry(route) {</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Text(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"Product&nbsp;</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\"><span class=\"code-snippet__subst\">${route.id}</span></span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">&nbsp;\"</span>)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">else</span>&nbsp;-&gt; NavEntry(<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">Unit</span>) { Text(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"Unknown route:&nbsp;</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\"><span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">$route</span></span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"</span>) }</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">)</span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;width: auto;height: auto;margin-left: 15px;border-left: 1px dotted rgb(70, 70, 70);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;line-height: 0;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 14px 0% -7px;transform: translate3d(-4px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <p style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 7px;width: 7px;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 3px 0px inset;\">\n         <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <div style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <div style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">开始使用并分享反馈</span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u20ia\"><span leaf=\"\">首先，您可以查看<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">开发者文档</span>以及<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">操作指南</span>，其中提供了以下示例:</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u1u5s\">常见导航界面，例如导航边栏或导航栏</span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u1nh8\">条件导航，例如登录流程</span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1uh8c\"><span leaf=\"\">使用&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">Scenes</span>&nbsp;的自定义布局</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">开发者文档</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://goo.gle/nav3\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gle/nav3</a></span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">操作指南</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\">h</span><span leaf=\"\">ttps://github.com/android/nav3-recipes</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u10uh\">我们计划在未来为更复杂的用例提供代码示例、技术文档和文章。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u12z2\"><span leaf=\"\">Nav3 目前处于 Alpha 阶段，这意味着我们可能会根据反馈修改 API。如果您有任何问题或反馈，欢迎<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">分享给我们</span>:</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/new?component=1750212&amp;template=2102223\" target=\"_blank\">https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/new?component=1750212&amp;template=2102223</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1u45p\">Nav3 为在 Compose 应用中构建现代导航提供了灵活而强大的基础。我们非常期待看到您借此打造的精彩作品。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdwzgo1ue2w\"><span leaf=\"\">您可以在&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">io.google</span>&nbsp;上查看所有 Google I/O 2025 的精彩更新。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">io.google</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://io.google/2025/?utm_source=blogpost&amp;utm_medium=pr&amp;utm_campaign=event&amp;utm_content\" target=\"_blank\">https://io.google/2025/?utm_source=blogpost&amp;utm_medium=pr&amp;utm_campaign=event&amp;utm_content</a></span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Jetpack Navigation 3 是专为 Compose 设计的全新导航库，采用声明式模型，赋予开发者对返回堆栈的完全控制，并支持自适应布局。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Jetpack Navigation 3 是专为 Compose 设计的全新导航库，采用声明式模型，赋予开发者对返回堆栈的完全控制，并支持自适应布局。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了谷歌推出的全新导航库 Jetpack Navigation 3 (Nav3)，旨在解决旧版 Navigation 库 (Nav2) 在与 Jetpack Compose 结合使用时的限制，如返回堆栈状态间接观察和多窗格布局实现的困难。Nav3 基于开发者掌控返回堆栈、开放可扩展、模块化构建等原则设计，采用声明式编程模型和 Compose 状态。它提供了内置动画、自适应布局 (通过 Scenes API)、状态范围限定和模块化等关键功能，并提供了基本代码示例和开发者文档链接，鼓励开发者开始使用并提供反馈。Nav3 旨在为 Compose 应用构建现代、灵活的导航系统。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "开发者完全掌控返回堆栈，实现灵活的导航管理。",
      "explanation": "Nav3 将返回堆栈暴露为可观察的 Compose 状态列表 (SnapshotStateList)，允许开发者直接添加或删除项目，从而实现更灵活和可预测的导航行为，解决 Nav2 间接观察的限制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "库设计开放且可扩展，告别黑盒操作，提供更多定制能力。",
      "explanation": "Nav3 秉承开放性和可扩展性原则，提供更小巧的组件和实用的默认设置，开发者可以深入到更低的层级，创建自定义组件和行为，增强了库的灵活性和开发者的掌控力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "支持自适应布局和丰富的动画效果，提升用户体验和适应性。",
      "explanation": "通过灵活布局 API (Scenes) 可在同一布局中渲染多个目标位置，轻松切换单/多窗格。同时内置过渡动画和预测性返回支持，并提供灵活 API 自定义动画，提升了 UI 的适应性和交互的流畅性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Nav3 采用了声明式编程模型和 Compose 状态作为其基本构建模块。",
    "作为开发者，您将拥有并控制返回堆栈，而不是将控制权交给库。",
    "Nav3 并没有将所有行为嵌入到库中，而是提供了更小巧的组件，您可以组合这些组件来创建更复杂的功能。",
    "通过使用灵活布局 API (名为 Scenes)，您可在同一布局中渲染多个目标位置 (例如，大屏设备上的列表-详情布局)。"
  ],
